{
  "stem": "14091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Germans attacked the Russians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And at that time, really hell break-- broke out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Everybody ran.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My brothers-- we had horses and buggies-- my brothers wanted very badly that we should run, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But my father thought that we suffered enough, and it wouldn't be prudent, it wouldn't be smart that we should also run with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[SIGHS] The Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And when everything really started, it took a very short while, maybe a month or so, that they tried to take most of the people from the vicinity and tried to organize a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Not only the Germans, but the collaborators-- the people who were friends of all of us, supposedly-- became the police and the gendarme.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They did the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They brought from everywhere, from all the farms that some Jews had farms, lived all around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They brought them and the ghetto was organized in the place where our house stood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So our houses were included in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They put barbed wire all around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And this was already becoming-- this was already in the fall of I think of '42, no, maybe '41.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And-- yeah, it was in '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it became-- it started to be cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They threw us in-- each family had only one room, we slept on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It start being very cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We didn't have any wood or any fire to-- to warm ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they didn't let the people bring many things when they collected them and just threw them into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our whole family was together at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we took one of the biggers-- the bigger rooms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were all together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, my sister was married, had a boy, a baby.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
